{"id": "1734", "post": "<div class=\"post-1734 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-fehosting-com tag-los-angeles tag-openvz\" id=\"post-1734\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/forever-hosting-19-95year-256mb-openvz-vps-in-la/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Forever Hosting \u2013 $19.95/Year 256MB OpenVZ VPS in LA</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/fehosting-com/\" rel=\"tag\">fehosting.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/los-angeles/\" rel=\"tag\">los angeles</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> April 4, 2011 @ 12:57 pm, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><div class=\"notice\"><b>Updated February 2012</b>: Forever Hosting is unfortunately, not forever. It died somewhere in 2011, and it\u2019s homepage has been showing cPanel login page for a while.</div><p><a href=\"http://www.fehosting.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/images/fehosting.jpg\" alt=\"Forever Hosting\" class=\"screenshot\"></a> Michael from <a href=\"http://www.fehosting.com/\"><b>Forever Hosting</b></a> emailed me a few days ago about their special promotion on their Los Angeles nodes. Works out to be <b>$19.95/Year</b> (~$1.66/month), or $35/2 years. Use <a href=\"https://billing.fehosting.com/order/?pid=70&amp;skip=1\">this link to order</a>, and here is the spec</p><ul><li>256MB guaranteed/512MB burstable memory</li><li>35GB storage</li><li>500GB/month data transfer</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li></ul><p>Servers based in Los Angeles CA (US West Coast, good for Asia-Pacific users). Forever Hosting actually <em>hasn\u2019t been around forever</em> \u2014 they were founded in 2010 with history back in 2008. Mixed reviews here at LowEndBox.com, but Michael has been quite active replying comments <a href=\"/blog/forever-hosting-3-60-512mb-openvz-vps/\">on their previous offer</a>.</p><p>Domain registered August 2010, NS on adjacent IP addresses. Old offer pages on WHT have all disappeared, and their user account there is inaccessible \u2014 which could mean <em>bad things</em> if WHT moderators did some research and find something fishy.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fforever-hosting-19-95year-256mb-openvz-vps-in-la%2F&amp;t=Forever%20Hosting%20-%20%2419.95%2FYear%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20LA\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Forever%20Hosting%20-%20%2419.95%2FYear%20256MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20LA&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fforever-hosting-19-95year-256mb-openvz-vps-in-la%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/s